caption: An underwater scene featuring a diver swimming away from the camera. The diver's light illuminates the murky, teal water, revealing a glimpse of the rocky bottom below. The overall image is blurry, creating a sense of mystery and the unknown depths of the underwater world.
technicalities: The image is blurry and dominated by dark, deep teal water. A white streak of light cuts through the upper left quadrant. The lower right portion is out of focus with a mix of yellowish-green and teal.
life_forms: swimming away from the camera with a light
